metadata.name: Soupa Bowl Ticket #1
metadata.description: This ticket entitles the holder to all the glory that comes with owning and designing a 1/1 OctopuoS. The holder has the opportunity to work with the OctopuoS artist, 4th Culture to design their 1/1 OctopuoS. Once the design is finalised, it will be added to the OctopuoS collection and the complete 1/1 OctopuoS token will be airdropped
